    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo in concours-level condition. This A80 chassis features the legendary 2JZ-GTE power plant, retaining its factory sequential twin-turbocharger configuration and original intercooler ducting. Power is delivered through the robust Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip rear differential. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, utilizing the original double-wishbone setup for precise kinematic feedback. Every factory weld and VIN tag is accounted for, ensuring structural integrity. Mechanically flawless with zero parasitic draws or fluid seepage, this unit represents the pinnacle of JDM engineering in its most unadulterated form.",
